606
00:48:31,350 --> 00:48:33,790
Okay, I get it.

607
00:48:33,790 --> 00:48:37,460
From this day, let's cut our ties.

608
00:48:37,460 --> 00:48:39,630
Goodbye for real.

609
00:48:39,630 --> 00:48:42,090
Bye-bye.

610
00:48:42,090 --> 00:48:46,330
