630
00:49:57,470 --> 00:49:59,730
You do what you want to do about with them.

631
00:49:59,730 --> 00:50:02,990
Right now...

632
00:50:02,990 --> 00:50:08,100
I can't care anything about Joon Oh and Mi Rim.

633
00:50:09,720 --> 00:50:12,990
Soo Chul can't do this to me.

634
00:50:12,990 --> 00:50:15,570
How can he do this to me? How?

635
00:50:15,570 --> 00:50:18,970
How can he do this to me at all..?

636
00:50:18,970 --> 00:50:22,810
Younger-sister-in-law...

637
00:50:24,440 --> 00:50:27,010
What's going on right now?

638
00:50:44,700 --> 00:50:46,700
Ajussi.

639
00:50:48,180 --> 00:50:50,810
What are you doing?

640
00:50:50,810 --> 00:50:53,780
Did I ask for stuff like this?

641
00:50:53,780 --> 00:50:59,340
I saw you on the street by chance.

642
00:50:59,340 --> 00:51:00,880
That's how I found out you lived here.

643
00:51:00,880 --> 00:51:04,420
That's what I mean. Why are you bringing stuff like this?

644
00:51:04,420 --> 00:51:07,530
Please take them all back.

645
00:51:07,530 --> 00:51:09,130
And don't ever come back again.

646
00:51:09,130 --> 00:51:10,880
Sarah.

647
00:51:10,880 --> 00:51:14,130
I said take it back. I'm not a beggar.

648
00:51:14,130 --> 00:51:20,290
If you keep doing this, I can't live here anymore.

649
00:51:20,290 --> 00:51:26,310
Even if you saw me, you should've ignored me. Why are you coming here and making me more pitiful?

650
00:51:26,310 --> 00:51:30,700
Why are you being nice to someone like me?

651
00:51:30,700 --> 00:51:31,810
Why?

652
00:51:31,810 --> 00:51:34,590
