653
00:51:34,590 --> 00:51:39,170
So you should focus on your health and nothing else.

654
00:51:39,170 --> 00:51:45,040
Whenever bad memories come up, look at the flowers and think only nice things.

655
00:51:45,040 --> 00:51:49,780
I will only go this far.

656
00:51:49,780 --> 00:51:52,350
I will just do this.

657
00:51:52,350 --> 00:51:57,340
I don't want to receive things like these from you.

658
00:51:57,340 --> 00:52:00,710
Sarah.

659
00:52:00,740 --> 00:52:04,500
If you have any feelings of regret toward me,

660
00:52:04,500 --> 00:52:11,910
if you feel any sympathy for the baby, please let me do so.

661
00:52:11,910 --> 00:52:14,280
Please stay well as I've asked.

662
00:52:14,280 --> 00:52:19,810
