663
00:52:19,810 --> 00:52:23,170
I will never forgive you.

664
00:52:24,950 --> 00:52:27,390
Okay?

665
00:52:31,500 --> 00:52:35,370
What do you want me to do?

666
00:52:54,130 --> 00:52:58,420
- Noona.
- Come sit here, Soo Chul.

667
00:52:58,420 --> 00:53:00,690
What's going on?

668
00:53:00,690 --> 00:53:05,410
Oh my world, are you having an affair with that woman, Anna Kim?

669
00:53:05,410 --> 00:53:07,530
Is that really true?

670
00:53:07,530 --> 00:53:10,630
What are you talking about it?

671
00:53:10,630 --> 00:53:12,070
An affair?

672
00:53:12,070 --> 00:53:14,380
Is it not true?

673
00:53:14,380 --> 00:53:17,850
Then why are you shopping at a market with her?

674
00:53:17,850 --> 00:53:20,050
And go in and out of her home?

675
00:53:20,050 --> 00:53:24,830
Your wife is bedridden right now.

676
00:53:24,830 --> 00:53:27,210
What?

677
00:53:29,990 --> 00:53:32,310
Please tell me the truth.

678
00:53:32,310 --> 00:53:35,590
Are you having an affair with her?

679
00:53:35,590 --> 00:53:37,500
No, it's not that.

680
00:53:37,500 --> 00:53:43,110
