695
00:54:55,600 --> 00:55:01,720
Is that really true?

696
00:55:01,720 --> 00:55:04,030
Yes.

697
00:55:04,030 --> 00:55:09,850
But, she wants to die without having the operation.

698
00:55:09,850 --> 00:55:14,090
