699
00:55:14,090 --> 00:55:19,140
Honey, don't we have to keep people alive?

700
00:55:19,140 --> 00:55:25,090
Maybe because of the overwhelming guilt she feels about abandoning Dan Dan.

701
00:55:25,090 --> 00:55:26,990
She wants to die without an operation.

702
00:55:26,990 --> 00:55:29,810
