703
00:55:29,810 --> 00:55:31,990
That's all.

704
00:55:31,990 --> 00:55:35,120
Oh, my goodness. What is going on with all this?

705
00:55:35,120 --> 00:55:37,370
Yes.

706
00:55:37,370 --> 00:55:42,370
