718
00:56:22,220 --> 00:56:25,230
He's acting so strange.

719
00:56:26,730 --> 00:56:28,690
If you see her again,

720
00:56:28,690 --> 00:56:32,250
I will not leave you alone! Ever!

721
00:56:36,230 --> 00:56:40,610
My goodness. What is going on?

722
00:56:49,820 --> 00:56:54,040
Now I'm really sick of you.

723
00:56:54,040 --> 00:56:56,520
Don't ever show in front of me again and get lost.

724
00:56:56,520 --> 00:57:00,720
Get away from us and from this world!

725
00:57:02,290 --> 00:57:06,940
I don't ever want to see you again.

726
00:57:12,910 --> 00:57:18,170
