734
00:58:38,040 --> 00:58:40,420
Disappeared?

735
00:58:42,270 --> 00:58:47,170
What should I do? I think it's because of me.

736
00:58:47,170 --> 00:58:51,750
I came by here earlier and told her to disappear.

737
00:58:51,750 --> 00:58:55,930
