739
00:58:58,370 --> 00:59:01,270
No, it's not.

740
00:59:01,270 --> 00:59:04,570
I'm sure she will be in touch. So don't worry about it, and let's go home.

741
00:59:04,570 --> 00:59:12,290
If she doesn't get in touch and doesn't get her operation, she might be in trouble.

