743
00:59:19,200 --> 00:59:21,810
Why did she come here and make our lives miserable?

744
00:59:21,810 --> 00:59:27,600
I hate CEO Anna so much.

745
00:59:31,850 --> 00:59:34,250
Dan Dan.

746
00:59:35,910 --> 00:59:39,540
Please stop...

747
00:59:39,540 --> 00:59:44,040
hating your mom.

748
00:59:46,710 --> 00:59:49,250
Stop hating her?

