770
01:01:52,940 --> 01:01:56,260
Ms. Park would never do something like that.

771
01:02:00,500 --> 01:02:05,510
CEO Anna, what's wrong?

772
01:02:08,300 --> 01:02:14,160
I just thought of my old times.

773
01:02:14,160 --> 01:02:16,680
Ms. Park.

774
01:02:18,390 --> 01:02:22,090
Is it okay if I hug you for once?

775
01:02:24,210 --> 01:02:26,130
Yes.

776
01:02:33,710 --> 01:02:36,920
Thank you, Ms. Park.

777
01:02:46,500 --> 01:02:49,820
[Chairman]

778
01:02:51,570 --> 01:02:53,790
Yes, it's me.

779
01:02:53,790 --> 01:02:58,250
Ms. Park, I'm calling to say goodnight.

780
01:02:58,250 --> 01:03:02,490
Ms. Park, please dream of me tonight.

