What should I do?

783
01:03:10,580 --> 01:03:14,120
Ms. Park. What's wrong?

784
01:03:14,120 --> 01:03:16,380
What happened?

785
01:03:24,850 --> 01:03:31,360
CEO Anna has pancreatic cancer?

786
01:03:31,360 --> 01:03:33,670
Really?

787
01:03:33,670 --> 01:03:35,420
Yes.

788
01:03:37,430 --> 01:03:42,850
If she doesn't get an operation, she has less than six months to live.

789
01:03:42,850 --> 01:03:45,460
But what should I do, Chairman?

790
01:03:45,460 --> 01:03:52,250
I didn't know that, and I told her to disappear from this world.

791
01:03:52,250 --> 01:03:55,050
I hurt her with those terrible words.

792
01:03:55,050 --> 01:03:58,300
What if something bad happens to her because of me?

793
01:03:58,300 --> 01:04:00,410
What do I do?

794
01:04:00,410 --> 01:04:03,450
I really don't know what to do.

795
01:04:03,450 --> 01:04:07,140
I hate her, and then I pity her.

796
01:04:07,140 --> 01:04:14,260
I can't tell if I should hate her or pity her.

797
01:04:14,260 --> 01:04:20,490
If you want to hate her, hate her. Pity her if you want to.

798
01:04:20,490 --> 01:04:24,060
You do whatever you feel like it.

799
01:04:24,060 --> 01:04:26,700
It's all okay.

800
01:04:26,700 --> 01:04:29,100
It's okay.

801
01:04:54,850 --> 01:04:57,640
What are you doing?

802
01:04:57,640 --> 01:05:01,180
Are you worried about her because she disappeared?

803
01:05:01,180 --> 01:05:07,830
You can't sleep because you worry that she might have died somewhere?

804
01:05:07,840 --> 01:05:12,420
Why are you acting like this? Why are you yelling when everyone's asleep?

805
01:05:12,420 --> 01:05:15,790
Does it break your heart that much that she's ill?

806
01:05:15,790 --> 01:05:20,420
Why don't you go and live with her then? Why are you living with me!

807
01:05:20,420 --> 01:05:25,350
If you are going to be like this, just divorce me. You bastard!

808
01:05:25,350 --> 01:05:28,190
Aigo, Yeon Sil!

809
01:05:28,190 --> 01:05:32,500
What are you doing at the crack of dawn?

810
01:05:32,510 --> 01:05:40,800
Mom. He can't sleep because he's worried about that woman.

811
01:05:40,800 --> 01:05:43,600
I can't live with him anymore.

812
01:05:43,600 --> 01:05:47,980
Have you ever worried for me like that, ever?

813
01:05:47,980 --> 01:05:54,750
When I left home after losing the house, he never even looked for me.

814
01:05:54,750 --> 01:06:00,090
But now, he's so worried that that woman might have died somewhere.

815
01:06:00,090 --> 01:06:02,860
How can I live with him after seeing this?

816
01:06:02,860 --> 01:06:05,560
Let's get divorced! Divorced!

817
01:06:05,560 --> 01:06:08,290
Please stop, Yeon Sil.

818
01:06:08,290 --> 01:06:13,640
What are you doing at this hour? Please stop it!

819
01:06:22,030 --> 01:06:25,400
Who raised Dan Dan when she abandoned her?

820
01:06:25,400 --> 01:06:31,330
Who saved you and Dan Dan when you tried to drown to death in the river?

821
01:06:31,330 --> 01:06:36,390
How can you do this to me? How?

822
01:06:36,390 --> 01:06:42,360
I want to die... I really want to die!

823
01:06:42,400 --> 01:06:47,180
If you're going to act like this, get out of here. Go live with her!

824
01:07:09,380 --> 01:07:11,230
Yes, hello?

825
01:07:11,230 --> 01:07:15,350
Hello? A woman came to my accommodation.

826
01:07:15,350 --> 01:07:18,210
And she looks like she's very ill, so I'm calling you.

827
01:07:18,210 --> 01:07:21,870
Do you know the owner of this phone very well?

828
01:07:21,870 --> 01:07:24,150
Yes, I'm her family.

829
01:07:24,150 --> 01:07:26,570
Then please come and get her right away.

830
01:07:26,570 --> 01:07:31,430
I called you because she won't go to the hospital, and I'm worried something will happen.

831
01:07:31,430 --> 01:07:35,710
I turned her phone on in secret to her.

832
01:07:35,710 --> 01:07:38,300
Thank you very much.

833
01:07:38,300 --> 01:07:40,890
Where are you located?

834
01:07:43,690 --> 01:07:47,320
Where are you going this early? Are you going to that woman again?

835
01:07:47,320 --> 01:07:50,290
Honey, they found CEO Anna.

836
01:07:50,290 --> 01:07:52,830
She's in bad shape. I will be right back.

837
01:07:52,830 --> 01:07:57,930
Why are you going there? What are you to her?

838
01:07:57,960 --> 01:08:00,520
Please calm down.

839
01:08:00,520 --> 01:08:06,030
She only has six months to live. What can they do together?

840
01:09:07,440 --> 01:09:09,900
Soo Chul.

841
01:09:09,900 --> 01:09:13,430
How did you find me here?

842
01:09:13,430 --> 01:09:18,850
What are you doing here when you are getting surgery next week?

843
01:09:18,850 --> 01:09:20,920
Let's go back to Seoul together.

844
01:09:20,920 --> 01:09:25,580
I came here to be alone.

845
01:09:27,130 --> 01:09:30,060
Don't mind me and go home.

846
01:09:30,060 --> 01:09:32,910
You can't stay here like that.

847
01:09:32,910 --> 01:09:35,260
Let's go.

848
01:09:41,990 --> 01:09:46,890
Please don't mind whether I live or die.

849
01:09:46,890 --> 01:09:50,200
I won't go with you.

850
01:09:51,950 --> 01:09:57,470
Is that because of what my wife did?

851
01:09:57,470 --> 01:10:00,610
She misunderstood because she didn't know you were sick.

852
01:10:00,610 --> 01:10:01,920
So--

853
01:10:01,920 --> 01:10:06,280
Your wife has every right to act that way.

854
01:10:06,280 --> 01:10:11,460
I don't want to create trouble in your home.

855
01:10:11,460 --> 01:10:17,030
Because you are acting like this, I came here so that I can't see you.

856
01:10:18,780 --> 01:10:21,780
Ji Young.

857
01:10:21,780 --> 01:10:24,390
Why are you being stubborn?

858
01:10:24,390 --> 01:10:27,630
If you do this, you'll make Dan Dan sad.

859
01:10:27,630 --> 01:10:30,960
Do you know how much she cried?

860
01:10:30,960 --> 01:10:35,230
Did Dan Dan cry?

861
01:10:35,230 --> 01:10:37,680
Because of me?

862
01:10:37,680 --> 01:10:39,660
Yes.

863
01:10:41,230 --> 01:10:46,930
So, let's go back.

864
01:10:46,930 --> 01:10:49,650
Let me take you home.

865
01:10:49,650 --> 01:10:55,140
Please, I beg you.

866
01:11:02,100 --> 01:11:04,370
Yeon Sil.

867
01:11:06,990 --> 01:11:12,100
Please forgive me just once.

868
01:11:15,370 --> 01:11:23,490
Please let me go to her.

869
01:11:23,490 --> 01:11:31,480
Just while she's getting her surgery, please allow me to be with her.

870
01:11:31,480 --> 01:11:34,920
Please.

871
01:11:34,940 --> 01:11:38,450
I beg you.

872
01:11:38,450 --> 01:11:48,050
Are you saying... you want to abandon me?

873
01:11:48,050 --> 01:11:53,170
Do you want to end it with me?

874
01:12:05,110 --> 01:12:12,740
♫ Why do you run away, love, like a shy child ♫

875
01:12:12,740 --> 01:12:19,530
♫  In case I lose it I hold it tight ♫

876
01:12:19,530 --> 01:12:26,710
♫  But love always runs away, chased by longing  ♫

877
01:12:26,710 --> 01:12:33,410
♫ It would be nice to take a break  ♫

878
01:12:33,410 --> 01:12:41,530
♫ I have to abandon the longing and the grieves  ♫

879
01:12:41,530 --> 01:12:42,880
♫  What am I looking  ♫

880
01:12:42,880 --> 01:12:45,580
[Young Lady and Gentleman]

881
01:12:45,580 --> 01:12:48,010
Chairman, where are we going today?

882
01:12:48,010 --> 01:12:49,170
We are going for lunch.

883
01:12:49,170 --> 01:12:50,850
- Dan Dan.
- Two of you, enjoy your lunch.

884
01:12:50,850 --> 01:12:55,010
Please don't misunderstand. I didn't ask Young Gook to do it.

885
01:12:55,010 --> 01:12:57,150
Where did he go in the middle of the night?

886
01:12:57,150 --> 01:12:59,180
Mi Sook, I can't get hold of Sarah.

887
01:12:59,180 --> 01:13:00,860
Can you find my Sarah for me?

888
01:13:00,860 --> 01:13:03,370
How can I know where Sarah is?

889
01:13:03,370 --> 01:13:05,750
It's been a long time since she left my house.

890
01:13:05,750 --> 01:13:07,660
Let's go to Vietnam together.

891
01:13:07,660 --> 01:13:10,500
I can take care of you and our baby.

892
01:13:10,500 --> 01:13:13,420
We can start afresh without anyone knowing.

893
01:13:13,420 --> 01:13:16,260
Of all the people, I thought you would understand my feelings.

894
01:13:16,260 --> 01:13:17,380
I'm sorry, Mom.

895
01:13:17,380 --> 01:13:20,490
Did you think I'd stop you from coming here if you told me?

896
01:13:20,490 --> 01:13:23,990
I hate CEO Anna very much, but I pity her too.

897
01:13:23,990 --> 01:13:25,850
Can't you understand me just once?

898
01:13:25,850 --> 01:13:27,120
Mom!

899
01:13:27,120 --> 01:13:29,600
♫ It would be nice to take a break  ♫
